\begin_layout Definition

\emph on
Sigma algebra.

\emph default
 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{A}$
\end_inset

 is a sigma algebra on a nonempty set 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

 iff all of the following are true:
\end_layout

