\begin_layout Definition

\emph on
Measure space.

\emph default
 A measure on a 
\begin_inset Formula $ $
\end_inset

measurable space 
\begin_inset Formula $(X,\mathcal{A})$
\end_inset

 is a function 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu:\mathcal{A}\rightarrow\mathbb{R}\cup\{\infty\}$
\end_inset

 such that
\end_layout

