\end_inset

 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $s\in\mathcal{A}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\mu(\emptyset)=0$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\mu$
\end_inset

 is countably additive, that is, if 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{I}$
\end_inset

 is countable and 
\begin_inset Formula $s_{i}\in\mathcal{A}$
\end_inset

