 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $i\neq j$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $i,j\in\mathcal{I}$
\end_inset

, then 
\begin_inset Formula \[
\mu\left(\bigcup_{i\in\mathcal{I}}s_{i}\right)=\sum_{i\in\mathcal{I}}\mu(s_{i}).\]

