 is the unique measure on 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{A}'$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu'(s)=\mu(s)$
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $s\in\mathcal{A}$
\end_inset

.
